## Jenkins Pipeline Reference: Dynamic Pods and Execution Templates
This guide details three foundational execution methodologies for Jenkins pipelines within your cluster: Ephemeral Kubernetes Pods, Dedicated Host Slaves, and Parameterized Cron Automation.
------------------------------
## 1.1.1. Template 1: Ephemeral Kubernetes Pod (Dynamic Agent)
This methodology spins up an isolated, temporary pod template in your Kubernetes cluster that mounts core tool shares (/x/eng/*) via host paths. The entire lifecycle terminates instantly when the pipeline completes.
