   1. Log into your team's Jenkins master URL.
   2. Select Dashboard ➔ New Item, type a unique job name, choose Pipeline, and click OK.
   3. Select the Pipeline tab at the top of the configuration sheet.
   4. (Optional) Select This project is parameterized and configure two string parameter blocks: PARAM1 and PARAM2. If skipped, remember to remove the parameter reference echo hooks from the code block below.
   5. Paste the following configuration directly into your Jenkins script block and click Save:

